<BaseLayout title="Captioning Images for LoRA Training" description="Write clear captions for LoRA training images." canonicalPath="/lora/captioning/"><article class="content-section article-body"><h1>Captioning Images for LoRA Training</h1><p>Captions should name the intended trigger and describe visible details. Mention pose, outfit, object features, scene, and style when they matter.</p><p>Avoid private identity cues, real-person names, protected character names, and brands. Captions should help the model learn lawful visual concepts, not impersonation.</p></article></BaseLayout>
